earlier at Labolo tented camp on the national park’s island, however
only one managed to clear the area safely,’’ the statement added. The wreckage of the helicopter was recovered in the early hours of Monday. The cause of the accident remains unknown. Cairo - An Egyptian Judge ordered six people to be remanded in custody for a… By SundiataPOST, Abuja The Joint Task Force (JTF) on Saturday in Kano said it had… By Isaac Aregbesola Abuja - Ukraine says five years of Russian aggression and forceful occupation…